channel.title: What the hell does this mean?
channel.description:
Well I was trying to add a real skillcape and I know the code, so I added it to the Item thing. I added it's number ID, the name, and it Examine phrase. But now when I run my server it says this:
[url=http://img.draynor.net][img]http://img.draynor.net/uploads/c09841bd0d.bmp[/img][/url]
Then when I try to log onto my server it loads the screen and it's all black and then it says "Connection Lost" and then I try to log back in and it doesn't work.
What do I do?
